What are the direct costs and what are the indirect costs?

28:10.000 --> 28:15.000
Direct costs to prepare the tax report.

28:15.000 --> 28:17.000
What is needed?

28:17.000 --> 28:23.000
Paper, computer and the work of an accountant.

